# Important Definitions

## Git

Distributed Version Control System.

---

## GitHub

Cloud platform that hosts Git repositories.

---

## Commit

A snapshot of the project saved in the local repository.

---

## Push

Uploads committed changes to GitHub.

---

## Pull

Downloads the latest changes from GitHub.

---

## Clone

Copies a remote repository to the local computer.

---

## Branch

An independent line of development.

---

## Merge

Combines changes from one branch into another.

